plan Booster's put
together...<NOD<CLO<FAO0000<WAI0010<FON0202:0001
<TRA0084:0203:0025:0010
#0203
<KEY<CMU0023<FAI0000<WAI0020
<MSG<FAC0001So here's the deal.<NOD
Momorin, Itoh, and Kazuma
are on their way over
right now.<NOD<CLR<FAC0006
Sue's family?<NOD<CLR<FAC0001They're on their way
over to pick her up.<NOD<FAC0003
They won't stay long, and
it's best they leave as
quickly as possible.<NOD<CLR<FAC0004According to Misery,
though...<NOD<FAC0002
Jenka's barrier hasn't
gotten any weaker.<NOD<CLR<FAC0006Huh?<NOD I thought Quote beat
those two spirit things
already?<NOD<CLR<FAC0003Right...<NOD But it looks like
Booster's theory was
true,<NOD and we need to
wake up Jenka to get
rid of them for good...<NOD<FAC0002
But the way things are, it
doesn't seem possible...<NOD<CLR<FAC0004Balrog, you and I are
going to wait here for
Kazuma.<NOD<CLR<FAC0006
What about Quote?<NOD<CLR<FAC0003Quote is going to head up
to the surface and turn
on the last teleporter.<NOD<FAC0002<ANP0210:0000:0000
I offered to do it myself,
but...<NOD<FAC0004 Booster insisted
you have far more
experience dealing with
the island.<NOD It's
imperative that that
teleporter gets turned on.<NOD<CLR<FAC0005I've been unarmed and no
help since we got here,
so I don't really mind...<NOD<CLR<FAC0006So, uh...<NOD<ANP0210:0000:0002<FAC0007<ANP0220:0030:0000 What do we do
after Quote turns it on?<NOD<CLR<FAC0003After he's done, we're
free to leave the island.<NOD<FAC0002
In fact, Booster stressed
that we do, as soon as
possible.<NOD<CMU0000<CLR<FAC0006
Huh?<NOD<CLR<FAC0004He's evacuating as many
people from the island as
he can.<NOD<CLR<FAC0003Jenka's magic has gotten
too unpredictable.<NOD<FAC0002
It's only a matter of
time before the island
falls apart...<NOD<CLO<WAI0020
<FAO0001<FOM0016<WAI0050<CMU0023<FAI0001<END
